snippet.title: C64 Longplay: Cyberworld (1984 Progressive Peripherals & Software)
snippet.description:
Requested by Dr. Abuze. This game is an early and fairly-dated Role Playing Game, but still pretty good for the time. I could find hardly any info on it online. Not a cover scan, review... nothing! Anyway, with a bit of map-making and note-taking I figured it out. Played on the easiest difficulty level so you probably get to do more with the objects on the higher ones.

ROM: http://www.gb64.com/game.php?id=11468&d=18&h=0
